-- Spain Cabinet to Examine Law on Budget Measures, Cinco Dias Says
-- B y   A n g e l i n e   B e n o i t
-- 2012-01-13T07:41:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-13/spain-cabinet-to-examine-law-on-budget-measures-cinco-dias-says.html
Spain ’s cabinet will examine today a
draft law to comply with a constitutional amendment on budget
discipline approved by parliament Sept. 2,  Cinco Dias  reported.  The amendment will fix spending limits for regions and
extend the central government’s control over their budgets, the
newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
